description:
Prefect is http://anidb.net/ch88461 [Ange]`s and http://anidb.net/ch88462 [Dorothy]`s former classmate from the spy-training school, the Farm, led by the http://anidb.net/ch92208 [Control].
Ange, Dorothy and http://anidb.net/ch88464 [Beatrice] were sent on a mission to steal secret documents from the First Lord of the Admiralty and Prefect was their insider as a fellow spy. However, their secondary mission was to check whether she was double agent, which turned out to be true. Before they could capture her, she committed suicide.
Source: Wikipedia, edited.
name: Iinchou
